.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, d&b, pop, salsa
City: liverpool, prague, nizza, paris
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
2. the fan of salsa is the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
4. the fan of d&b is the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the fan of pop is between the fan of classical and the fan of d&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | pop           | classical | salsa  |
| City         | liverpool | paris | prague   | nizza |

