.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, prince, bolivar, game
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the prince-smoker is the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the davidoff-smoker is between the person driving the bus and the bolivar-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | game   | prince | davidoff | bolivar      |
| Transport     | roller | bus    | motorbike  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, azure, mauve, ebony
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, snowmobile
1. the person driving the helicopter is the person who likes azure##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who likes mauve and the person driving the roller##2
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Color       | aquamarine | ebony | mauve     | azure   |
| Transport   | roller   | motorbike     | snowmobile | helicopter |

