.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
House: colonial, palace, cottage, farmhouse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, scooter, ship, van
1. the cottage house is between the person driving the boat and the colonial house##2
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the colonial house##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the colonial house##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the van##1
5. the colonial house is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| House         | palace | cottage | colonial | farmhouse |
| Transport   | boat         | van       | scooter    | ship         |

