.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, garlic, peach, plum
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, june, september, january
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person eating peach##1
3. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person eating garlic and the person who's birthday is in january##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | plum   | peach      | garlic   | avocado  |
| Birthday   | january | june | september | december |

