.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: apple, cauliflower, lime, onion
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bongani, chaman, dannemann
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is between the person eating onion and the person eating apple##2
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person eating apple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | apple     | cauliflower | onion   | lime        |
| Cigar   | tiparillo | chaman   | bongani | dannemann |

