.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, japanese, colombian, indonesian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, pop, punk, trance
1. the fan of punk is the japanese##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of trance##1
3. the fan of gospel is the nigerian##1
4. the colombian is the fan of pop##1
5. the fan of gospel is on the right of the indonesian##1
6. the fan of pop is between the japanese and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Nationality         | japanese | colombian | indonesian | nigerian |
| Music-Genre   | punk          | pop     | trance  | gospel     |

