2. the police-officer is between the person eating potato and the designer##2
3. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
4. the designer is on the left of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2        |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | designer | police-officer | musician | nurse     |
| Food   | papaya   | grapes    | potato   | banana |

