.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, zombie, martial-arts, sports
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, lizard, rabbit
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the lizard##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the goat and the person watching zombie movies##2
4. the owner of the rabbit is the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | zombie | western | martial-arts |
| Pet           | lizard  | rabbit  | goldfish | goat      |

