.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, family, zombie, scientific
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, golf, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is baseball##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
5. the person watching zombie movies is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific   | sports   | family | zombie |
| Sport         | baseball | basketball | rowing     | golf    |

